# ── Dual-use public-surface gating (do NOT publish raw) ──────────────────────
# Raw evaluation corpus: contains verbatim prompts (incl. select-agent sequences
# at the sequence-identifier levels) AND raw model responses (incl. hazard-mechanism
# text). Publish redacted, aggregate-only copies from pilot/results_public/ instead,
# generated by pilot/redact_results_for_public.py.
/pilot/results/
*.jsonl
# Exception: the curated, redacted refusal-outcomes table (safe aggregate; outcome
# labels only, no response text and no sequences) shipped for the HF dataset viewer.
!data/llm_sfm_refusal_trials.jsonl
# Materialized select-agent toxin sequences — ship the builder + GenBank accessions
# (pilot/build_dna_sequences.py) instead of the resolved sequences.
/pilot/dna_sequences.json
/pilot/recovery_*/
*.err
